        "I am writing this letter in connection with an oven toaster that I bought on 20th September from one of your branch in London.",
        "The problem is that I plugged in the oven upon I unboxed it at home and I realised that the oven was unable to warm up properly. I followed the instruction many times to make sure about the phasis of installation. Then, I phoned your customer service for an immediate help, but unfortunately there was no answer on your part.",
